    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Primarly used in film industry special effects, mattes are sheilds or masks placed in front of a camera's lens to block out part of the image being shot, for the purpose of shooting subsequent images which may be inserted into the blocked space. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000047994/Katz, The film encyclopedia (1998)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000045747/Singleton and Conrad, Filmmaker's Dictionary (2000)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lensmaskers gebruikt men voornamelijk in de filmindustrie voor speciale effecten. Men plaatst ze voor de lens van de camera om een deel van het beeld af te schermen. Vervolgens kan men andere beelden invoegen in het afgeschermde gedeelte.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>主要運用於拍攝電影特效；遮片是裝置於攝影鏡頭前的遮罩或遮蔽物，可遮蔽部分入鏡影像，並在遮蔽處填入後續拍攝的影像。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
